 paper and set aside.","Place chocolate into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer into a small bowl and set aside.","Place butter into mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/80°C\/speed 2<b>.","Add remaining crumble ingredients, including reserved chocolate, and mix <b>5 sec\/\/speed 2<b>. Transfer mixture onto prepared baking tray and spread evenly.","Bake for 15 minutes (160°C). Allow to cool, then crumble into a bowl and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Chocolate sauce","content":["Place chocolate into mixing bowl and grate <b>10 sec\/speed 8<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add cream and heat <b>2 min\/50°C\/speed 3<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside to cool completely. Clean and dry mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Assembly","content":["Place milk into mixing bowl and heat <b>5 min\/70°C\/speed 1<b>, or until temperature reaches 70°C.","Blend <b>20 sec\/speed 8<b>, placing simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid, to froth milk.","Remove glasses with custard from refrigerator. Pour a thin layer of reserved chocolate sauce into each glass, then top with reserved ice cream, and sprinkle with reserved crumble. Top each glass with a layer of frothed milk foam and dust with cocoa powder. Serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Ice cream","content":["100 g dark chocolate, broken into pieces","200 g pouring (whipping) cream","300 g full cream milk","3 egg yolks","80 g white sugar","1 tsp vanilla bean paste","2 tbsp Kahlua®              (optional)"]},{"title":"Chocolate custard","content":["500 g cold water","2 titanium strength gelatine leaves","100 g dark chocolate, broken into pieces","500 g pouring (whipping) cream","3 tsp instant granulated coffee","1 tsp sugar","4 egg yolks"]},{"title":"Crumble","content":["80 g white chocolate, broken into pieces","20 g unsalted butter","20 g caster sugar","20 g flaked almonds","1 tbsp plain flour","1 tbsp cocoa powder","1 pinch salt"]},{"title":"Chocolate 